# Superstore Sales Analysis

## Project Overview
This project analyzes Superstore sales data to identify sales trends, regional performance, top-selling products, and seasonal patterns.

## Objectives
- Clean and prepare sales data
- Analyze sales performance
- Calculate KPIs
- Visualize sales trends
- Provide business recommendations

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Google Colab

## KPIs
- Total Revenue
- Average Order Value
- Profit Margin (Estimated)

## Visualizations
- Monthly Sales Trend
- Sales by Region
- Profit by Region
- Sales by Category
- Top 10 Products
- Bottom 10 Products
- Sales by Segment
- Top States by Sales

## Business Recommendations
1. Focus on high-performing products.
2. Increase stock before peak seasons.
3. Improve marketing in low-performing regions.
4. Increase average order value through cross-selling.
5. Optimize sales strategies using regional insights.
